Uses of Package
com.siperian.sif.message.metadata

  • Packages that use com.siperian.sif.message.metadata 
    Package Description
    com.siperian.sif.message.metadata
    Provides data objects for Siperian Hub meta-data - data describing objects defined in the Siperian Hub.
  • Classes in com.siperian.sif.message.metadata used by com.siperian.sif.message.metadata 
    Class and Description
    MetaDataBase
    Represents properties that are common to all metadata.

    MetaDataColumnBase

    MetaDataHmEntityType

    Represents a HM hierarchy.
    MetaDataHmPackage
    Represents a HM package.
    MetaDataHmProfile

    MetaDataHmRelationshipType
    Represents a HM relationship type.
    MetaDataHmSandbox
    Represents an HM Sandbox.
    MetaDataHmTypeBase
    Represents the base class for MetaDataHmRelationshipType and MetaDataHmEntityType.
    MetaDataMatchPathComponentFilter
    Represents metadata about a match path component filter of a match path component.
    MetaDataMatchRule

    MetaDataPackage
